itsky Act）推行。制裁名單顯示，新受制裁對象有3名個人，包括尹國駒（KOI, Wan Kuok），美方並將其稱為 &quot;Broken Tooth&quot;，另外兩名個人為1名吉爾吉斯（Kyrgyzstan）人及1名利比里亞（Liberia）人。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">財政部聲明稱，「崩牙駒」為中共政協成員，也是三合會組織「14K」頭目，為其中一個在全球最大的中國有組織犯罪集團，從事販毒、非法賭博、詐騙、人口販運等。</span><br />\n<br />\n制裁名單上也有3間受制裁企業或組織，包括設於<span class=\"red\">香港的東美投資集團有限公司、設於帛琉（Palau）的Palau China Hung-Mun Cultural Association，以及設於柬埔寨的世界洪門歷史文化協會，美方把這3間公司列為與「崩牙駒」有聯繫。</span><br />\n<br />\n01唔貼link"},{"pid":"ac2e0150b7ccbdeefbb21e52927b9ca276eec601","tid":2318871,"uid":132486,"like":40,"dislike":2,"score":38,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T16:08:22.000Z","msg":"過氣柒頭好似學人幫共產黨搞黑底數碼貨幣"},{"pid":"096832a92c570f6d82d90b60da0731d0647e1693","tid":2318871,"uid":106544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T16:08:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9d640c96283bf54a6857c889fcc3c96121d7124","tid":2318871,"uid":166729,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T16:09:14.000Z","msg":"好似係一帶一路打手同洗黑錢?"},{"pid":"2178d1ccb1856c4fb94399c511d738fcb3e5c365","tid":2318871,"uid":310867,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"ac2e0150b7ccbdeefbb21e52927b9ca276eec601","tid":2318871,"uid":132486,"like":40,"dislike":2,"score":38,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T16:08:22.000Z","msg":"過氣柒頭好似學人幫共產黨搞黑底數碼貨幣"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T16:09:18.000Z","msg":"數碼人民幣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b4bec56a8c8511599abaa7960f99f5b03da681f","tid":2318871,"uid":72034,"like":87,"dislike":1,"score":86,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T16:09:23.000Z","msg":"包括尹國駒（KOI, Wan Kuok），美方並將其稱為 &quot;Broken Tooth&quot;，<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f84b3738781cecf67865d4cade07b5b9bfb3cc7f","tid":2318871,"uid":227801,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"quote":{"pid":"a7f907b24fb7da73ba0681d30aa90f22f67856a9","tid":2318871,"uid":14494,"like":54,"dislike":4,"score":